<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8272550>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–5. Zercoseius luizdequeirozi n. sp., adult female. 1. Lateral (antiaxial) view of chelicera; 2. Hypostome; 3. Palptarsal claw; 4. Epistome; 5. Epistome (DIC micrograph)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8272550/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8272556>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6–8. Zercoseius luizdequeirozi n. sp., adult female. 6. Dorsal view of idiosoma; 7. Ornamentation of part of dorsal shield (DIC micrograph); 8. Setae J2–J4 (DIC micrograph)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8272556/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8272558>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9–13. Zercoseius luizdequeirozi n. sp., adult female. 9.Ventral view of idiosoma; 10. Sternal shield (DIC micrograph); 11. Fusion of peritrematic and exopodal plate near coxa IV (DIC micrograph); 12. Section of peritreme (DIC micrograph); 13. Sperm access system (variants)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8272558/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8272560>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14–17. Zercoseius luizdequeirozi n. sp., adult female. 14. Leg I: a, coxa-tibia; b, tip of tarsus with seta s; 15. Leg II: a, coxa-tibia; b, tarsus; 16. Leg III: a, coxa-tibia; b, tarsus; 17. Leg IV: a, coxa-tibia; b, tarsus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8272560/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

